              <property name="toolTip">
               <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p&gt;If checked, will plot a linear regression line in the plot (only 2D cases), showing general correlation of data between the two chosen order parameters.&lt;br/&gt;Plots a legend in the plot, with the linear function derived from the regression and the &amp;quot;R squared&amp;quot;-value of correlation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
              </property>
