             </spacer>
            </item>
            <item>
             <widget class="QSpinBox" name="resSpinBox">
              <property name="toolTip">
               <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p&gt;Used as:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;1. The resolution used by density plots to map all data values to a grid of size N*N, and the density of each gridpoint calculated and mapped.&lt;br/&gt;2. The resolution of a similar grid as in 1., but instead of calculating (counting) number of points at each gridpoint, attempt to interpolate the z-value at each gridpoint from all values located at the gridpoint in order to create a surface for plotting in Surface/Contour plots.&lt;br/&gt;3. As a value to be used for scatter plot dot size: scat_size = N/100&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
              </property>
              <property name="wrapping">
               <bool>false</bool>
              </property>
              <property name="minimum">
               <number>10</number>
              </property>
              <property name="maximum">
               <number>4000</number>
              </property>
              <property name="singleStep">
